<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="chocolate-n">chocolate <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tʃɒklət/    美 /'tʃɑːklət/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>巧克力；巧克力糖；巧克力饮料：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>bar / piece of chocolate</strong>
一块巧克力</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a box of chocolates
一盒巧克力</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a cup of hot chocolate
一杯巧克力热饮</p></div></div>